@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dsgunh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    v2 = (wp.exp(v2) + ((v0 + 0.20 / v1 + 0.89) - (v1 + 0.83 - v2 + 0.95)))
    v0 = (tmp + ((v0 + 0.96 / v0 + 0.92) / (tmp + 0.69 + v1 + 0.13)))
    v1 = (tmp + 0.01)
    data[tid] = v0
